text: In the 1991-92 Dutch football season, PSV Eindhoven competed in the Eredivisie. PSV won the Eredivisie that season and also participated in the European Cup going out in the second round to Anderlecht. ==First-team squad== ==Transfers== ===In=== * Tom Van Mol - Anderlecht U19 - Free * Wim de Ron - VV Dinteloord * Adri van Tiggelen - Anderlecht * Wim Kieft - Bordeaux * Ernest Faber - Nijmegen ===Out=== * John Bosman - Anderlecht - £810,000 * Raymond Beerens - Waalwijk - Loan * Jozef Chovanec - Sparta Praha * Geoffrey Prommanyon - FC Eindhoven - Loan * Ernest Faber - Sparta Rotterdam - Loan * Adick Koot - Cannes * Jan Nederburgh - Telstar ==Results== ===Eredivisie=== ===European Cup=== == References == Category:PSV Eindhoven seasons Category:Dutch football championship-winning seasons PSV Eindhoven
title: 1991–92 PSV Eindhoven season
